#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an7.57"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.57:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.57:0.2"
msgid "6. Abyākatavagga "
msgstr "6. The Undeclared Points "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.57:0.3"
msgid "57. Sīhasenāpatisutta "
msgstr "57. General Sīha "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an7.57:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "an7.57:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā vesāliyaṃ viharati mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Vesālī, at the Great Wood, in the hall with the peaked roof. "

msgctxt "an7.57:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho sīho senāpati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho sīho senāpati bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then General Sīha went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.57:1.4"
msgid "“sakkā nu kho, bhante, sandiṭṭhikaṃ dānaphalaṃ paññāpetun”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, can you point out a fruit of giving that’s apparent in the present life?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an7.57:2.1"
msgid "“Tena hi, sīha, taññevettha paṭipucchissāmi, yathā te khameyya tathā naṃ byākareyyāsi. "
msgstr "“Well then, Sīha, I’ll ask you about this in return, and you can answer as you like. "

msgctxt "an7.57:2.2"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, sīha, "
msgstr "What do you think, Sīha? "

msgctxt "an7.57:2.3"
msgid "idha dve purisā—"
msgstr "Consider two people. "

msgctxt "an7.57:2.4"
msgid "eko puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, eko puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato. "
msgstr "One is faithless, stingy, miserly, and abusive. One is a faithful donor who loves charity. "

#. VAR: kaṃ nu kho → kiṃ nu kho (mr)
msgctxt "an7.57:2.5"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, sīha, kaṃ nu kho arahanto paṭhamaṃ anukampantā anukampeyyuṃ: "
msgstr "Which do you think the perfected ones will show compassion for first?” "

msgctxt "an7.57:2.6"
msgid "‘yo vā so puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, yo vā so puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato’”ti? "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
#. VAR: kintaṃ → kinti (mr)
msgctxt "an7.57:3.1"
msgid "“Yo so, bhante, puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, kintaṃ arahanto paṭhamaṃ anukampantā anukampissanti. "
msgstr "“Why would the perfected ones first show compassion for the person who is faithless, stingy, miserly, and abusive? "

msgctxt "an7.57:3.2"
msgid "Yo ca kho so, bhante, puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato taṃyeva arahanto paṭhamaṃ anukampantā anukampeyyuṃ”. (1) "
msgstr "They’d show compassion first for the faithful donor who loves charity.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.80, sc4
msgctxt "an7.57:4.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, sīha, kaṃ nu kho arahanto paṭhamaṃ upasaṅkamantā upasaṅkameyyuṃ: "
msgstr "“Which do you think the perfected ones will first approach?” "

msgctxt "an7.57:4.2"
msgid "‘yo vā so puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, yo vā so puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato’”ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.57:4.3"
msgid "“Yo so, bhante, puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, kintaṃ arahanto paṭhamaṃ upasaṅkamantā upasaṅkamissanti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.57:4.4"
msgid "Yo ca kho so, bhante, puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato taṃyeva arahanto paṭhamaṃ upasaṅkamantā upasaṅkameyyuṃ”. (2) "
msgstr "“They’d first approach the faithful donor who loves charity.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an7.57:5.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, sīha, kassa nu kho arahanto paṭhamaṃ paṭiggaṇhantā paṭiggaṇheyyuṃ: "
msgstr "“Which do you think the perfected ones will receive alms from first?” "

msgctxt "an7.57:5.2"
msgid "‘yo vā so puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, yo vā so puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato’”ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.57:5.3"
msgid "“Yo so, bhante, puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, kintaṃ tassa arahanto paṭhamaṃ paṭiggaṇhantā paṭiggaṇhissanti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.57:5.4"
msgid "Yo ca kho so, bhante, puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato tasseva arahanto paṭhamaṃ paṭiggaṇhantā paṭiggaṇheyyuṃ”. (3) "
msgstr "“They’d receive alms first from the faithful donor who loves charity.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an7.57:6.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, sīha, kassa nu kho arahanto paṭhamaṃ dhammaṃ desentā deseyyuṃ: "
msgstr "“Which do you think the perfected ones will teach the Dhamma to first?” "

msgctxt "an7.57:6.2"
msgid "‘yo vā so puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, yo vā so puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato’”ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.57:6.3"
msgid "“Yo so, bhante, puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, kintaṃ tassa arahanto paṭhamaṃ dhammaṃ desentā desessanti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.57:6.4"
msgid "Yo ca kho so, bhante, puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato tasseva arahanto paṭhamaṃ dhammaṃ desentā deseyyuṃ”. (4) "
msgstr "“They’d first teach the Dhamma to the faithful donor who loves charity.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an7.57:7.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, sīha, kassa nu kho kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggaccheyya: "
msgstr "“Which do you think would get a good reputation?” "

msgctxt "an7.57:7.2"
msgid "‘yo vā so puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, yo vā so puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato’”ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.57:7.3"
msgid "“Yo so, bhante, puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, kintaṃ tassa kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggacchissati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.57:7.4"
msgid "Yo ca kho so, bhante, puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato tasseva kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggaccheyya”. (5) "
msgstr "“The faithful donor who loves charity would get a good reputation.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.81, sc8
msgctxt "an7.57:8.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, sīha, ko nu kho yaṃyadeva parisaṃ upasaṅkameyya, yadi khattiyaparisaṃ yadi brāhmaṇaparisaṃ yadi gahapatiparisaṃ yadi samaṇaparisaṃ visārado upasaṅkameyya amaṅkubhūto: "
msgstr "“Which do you think would enter any kind of assembly bold and assured, whether it’s an assembly of aristocrats, brahmins, householders, or ascetics?” "

msgctxt "an7.57:8.2"
msgid "‘yo vā so puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, yo vā so puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato’”ti? "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.57:8.3"
msgid "“Yo so, bhante, puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, kiṃ so yaṃyadeva parisaṃ upasaṅkamissati, yadi khattiyaparisaṃ yadi brāhmaṇaparisaṃ yadi gahapatiparisaṃ yadi samaṇaparisaṃ visārado upasaṅkamissati amaṅkubhūto. "
msgstr "“The faithful donor who loves charity would enter any kind of assembly bold and assured, whether it’s an assembly of aristocrats, brahmins, householders, or ascetics.” "

msgctxt "an7.57:8.4"
msgid "Yo ca kho so, bhante, puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato so yaṃyadeva parisaṃ upasaṅkameyya, yadi khattiyaparisaṃ yadi brāhmaṇaparisaṃ yadi gahapatiparisaṃ yadi samaṇaparisaṃ visārado upasaṅkameyya amaṅkubhūto”. (6) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an7.57:9.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, sīha, ko nu kho kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjeyya: "
msgstr "“When their body breaks up, after death, which do you think would be reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm?” "

msgctxt "an7.57:9.2"
msgid "‘yo vā so puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, yo vā so puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato’”ti? "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.57:9.3"
msgid "“Yo so, bhante, puriso assaddho maccharī kadariyo paribhāsako, kiṃ so kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjissati. "
msgstr "“Why would the person who is faithless, stingy, miserly, and abusive be reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm? "

msgctxt "an7.57:9.4"
msgid "Yo ca kho so, bhante, puriso saddho dānapati anuppadānarato so kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjeyya. (7) "
msgstr "The faithful donor who loves charity would, when their body breaks up, after death, be reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.82, sc10
msgctxt "an7.57:10.1"
msgid "Yānimāni, bhante, bhagavatā sandiṭṭhikāni dānaphalāni akkhātāni, nāhaṃ ettha bhagavato saddhāya gacchāmi. "
msgstr "When it comes to these fruits of giving that are apparent in the present life, I don’t have to rely on faith in the Buddha, "

msgctxt "an7.57:10.2"
msgid "Ahampi etāni jānāmi. "
msgstr "for I know them too. "

msgctxt "an7.57:10.3"
msgid "Ahaṃ, bhante, dāyako dānapati, maṃ arahanto paṭhamaṃ anukampantā anukampanti. "
msgstr "I’m a giver, a donor, and the perfected ones show compassion for me first. "

msgctxt "an7.57:10.4"
msgid "Ahaṃ, bhante, dāyako dānapati, maṃ arahanto paṭhamaṃ upasaṅkamantā upasaṅkamanti. "
msgstr "I’m a giver, and the perfected ones approach me first. "

msgctxt "an7.57:10.5"
msgid "Ahaṃ, bhante, dāyako dānapati, mayhaṃ arahanto paṭhamaṃ paṭiggaṇhantā paṭiggaṇhanti. "
msgstr "I’m a giver, and the perfected ones receive alms from me first. "

msgctxt "an7.57:10.6"
msgid "Ahaṃ, bhante, dāyako dānapati, mayhaṃ arahanto paṭhamaṃ dhammaṃ desentā desenti. "
msgstr "I’m a giver, and the perfected ones teach me Dhamma first. "

msgctxt "an7.57:10.7"
msgid "Ahaṃ, bhante, dāyako dānapati, mayhaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato: "
msgstr "I’m a giver, and I have this good reputation: "

msgctxt "an7.57:10.8"
msgid "‘sīho senāpati dāyako kārako saṅghupaṭṭhāko’ti. "
msgstr "‘General Sīha gives, serves, and attends on the Saṅgha.’ "

msgctxt "an7.57:10.9"
msgid "Ahaṃ, bhante, dāyako dānapati yaṃyadeva parisaṃ upasaṅkamāmi, yadi khattiyaparisaṃ … pe … yadi samaṇaparisaṃ visārado upasaṅkamāmi amaṅkubhūto. "
msgstr "I’m a giver, I enter any kind of assembly bold and assured, whether it’s an assembly of aristocrats, brahmins, householders, or ascetics. "

msgctxt "an7.57:10.10"
msgid "Yānimāni, bhante, bhagavatā sandiṭṭhikāni dānaphalāni akkhātāni, nāhaṃ ettha bhagavato saddhāya gacchāmi. "
msgstr "When it comes to these fruits of giving that are apparent in the present life, I don’t have to rely on faith in the Buddha, "

msgctxt "an7.57:10.11"
msgid "Ahampi etāni jānāmi. "
msgstr "for I know them too. "

msgctxt "an7.57:10.12"
msgid "Yañca kho maṃ, bhante, bhagavā evamāha: "
msgstr "But when the Buddha says: "

msgctxt "an7.57:10.13"
msgid "‘dāyako, sīha, dānapati kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjatī’ti. "
msgstr "‘When a giver’s body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm.’ I don’t know this, "

msgctxt "an7.57:10.14"
msgid "Etāhaṃ na jānāmi, ettha ca panāhaṃ, bhagavato saddhāya gacchāmī”ti. "
msgstr "so I have to rely on faith in the Buddha.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.57:10.15"
msgid "“Evametaṃ, sīha, evametaṃ, sīha. "
msgstr "“That’s so true, Sīha! That’s so true! "

msgctxt "an7.57:10.16"
msgid "Dāyako, sīha, dānapati kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjatī”ti. "
msgstr "When a giver’s body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.57:10.17"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

